Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:16.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Stop spoiling him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Rin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:20.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Shh. Don't be too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:22.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.98,0:00:28.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku, it's almost close to lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,and you're not waking him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,We just went on summer break. \NWhy are you letting him do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.94,0:00:36.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer break, Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:40.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to let him go \Nto sleep when he wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,and wake up and eat when he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:46.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to make Souta lazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:48.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You need to make sure he \Ngets up at a decent—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.07,0:00:51.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Souta. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting up, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:59.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all have a popsicle \Nlaying here together, Rin-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.82,0:01:01.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Sou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:04.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:10.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. I thought you were \Nmore together than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.97,0:01:13.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to Okiku-nee's \Nhouse in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:15.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess I just felt like relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:19.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess it's kind of cute to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:20.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,all defenseless like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:24.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone from Quest Dorm is headed back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:27.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to have him \Nhere than be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Mei would still be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:32.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,but Kurumiko had her go back home with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:37.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,She acts all tough, but Kurumiko \Nmanages to get to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:38.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:41.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Mei seems to have gotten friendlier lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:44.69,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Mei only lost her memories about
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:47.30,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,flags and the Council of the Seven Virtues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:50.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's some hidden \Nmeaning in all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:55.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:01:59.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:01.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse my entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.49,0:02:04.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Your entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:06.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,There is something that needs to \Nbe done before I'm overhauled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.94,0:02:09.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't bite your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:10.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:10.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:13.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait—
