Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:54.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:02.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my death flag had activated...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:10.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That means we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:17.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, when I said I missed you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:19.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri-chan flew off, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,She really did fly off. With jets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:25.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:26.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:30.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm going to \Nreturn to my maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten just how upper-class you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:41.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to think I live \Nin a different world than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akane-san, the Crawling Chaos, \Nwho's always by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:45.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:49.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You'll always be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:54.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:56.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:59.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're a kind girl, who \Nlooks great when she smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Not in a different world, or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:08.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:12.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,My heart will always be with yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:16.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,As along as you need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:21.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you're proposing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, not that I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's that I'd just feel bad about Rin-chan-senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:30.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and Mei-chan, and Megu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:32.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why don't you relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,There was a name in that list \Nthat shouldn't have been there, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:38.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, I'd feel bad for the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm not going to do something \Nwith you without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:45.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, I just left Rin-kun \Nand Okiku-nee there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.57,Contact_05:46,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(275,180)}He {\c&H0281E4&}contacts {\c&HE7C510&}them
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:49.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.22,0:05:51.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun! Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:52.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:53.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Okiku-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:54.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:56.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:59.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing getting \Nkidnapped without my permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:02.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, don't worry us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:04.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun went up to the stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:06.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing even happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have worried—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:10.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't worried at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Mei-oneechan was worried most \Nof all, until a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:17.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are Megumu and the others here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:20.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's because Okiku was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,worried and called everyone, crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:26.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is just getting crazier...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:31.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for all the trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:34.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri likes to cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:37.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm happy you missed Sou-kun while
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:38.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,we were on break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.07,0:06:42.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was all like we all left,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:44.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,and now we're back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:47.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you laughing, Kurumiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:52.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,No reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Akane-oneechan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:58.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,really does have a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't act stuck up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:04.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,and you're nice to me and Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:05.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumiko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to have all of you over today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:18.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I want all of you to have lots of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:26.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you eat this, Onii-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:28.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not well versed in \Ntable manners, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:32.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we should just copy Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:34.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:43.30,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seems to be staring at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:51.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Could you give Souta-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,a little extra roast beef?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:01.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Please cut a lot of roast beef for Sou-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Please give Souta a lot of roast beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:07.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,I want Souta-kun to have tons of roast beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:11.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Give Onii-chan an extra \Nhelping of roast beef!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I love roast beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:30.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing they have an \Noutdoor bath like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Megumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:42.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time you've \Ngotten in the bath with—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Souta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in the women's bath?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You pervert! Jerk! Voyeur!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:54.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is the men's bath, Rin-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,This is women's bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Akane and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:02.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean this is the women's bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Over this way, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:13.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to have a bath outdoors like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have called Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:18.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Our bath here is good for the skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think it helps a bad hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:22.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,It helps your skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,They've got a pool, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You saved me, Rin-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:32.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Souta saw me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Saw me naked...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:38.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get married now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:43.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess if no one else marries you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:44.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:48.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,You... bath and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:51.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-kun, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:55.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Rin-chan-senpai, you're here already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you splashing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's such a nice bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:03.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot myself and started \Nplaying around like a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Rin-oneechan sometimes acts like a kid—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,it's really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:10.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:12.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Mei-oneechan is the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:13.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:19.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,didn't get in the bath earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:24.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The bath here at the house has \Nset hours for men and women.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:28.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to tell Rin-chan-senpai \Nand Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Silly me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:33.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:53.47,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:54.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:56.30,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.92,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:01.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I-I guess you're lonely, too—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:03.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I mean bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:06.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll just have \Nto talk to you for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:07.77,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.60,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.42,0:11:10.90,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.54,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, it's Nanami-oneechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:14.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.41,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:19.34,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys all at Akane's house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,We're all sleeping over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:22.76,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.06,0:11:25.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, Akane-oneechan, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:30.89,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use me as a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:35.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Hatate Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for me to use
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,my Souta-kun pillow to win the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:45.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,When did you make that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:50.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You guys suck! Suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:54.76,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you don't get to join the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.98,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a pillow fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:05.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Out of battery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:32.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming such a long distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:37.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,As promised, we've come to \Nhave a pillow fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you having a pillow fight here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,She got mad at me for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:47.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:57.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Principality of Bladefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:02.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm sure you're \Nall tired from the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be on a train for three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:08.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to the capital, Twin Blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:13.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is going to be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:14.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to spend summer \Nbreak alone at the dorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice and peaceful country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:35.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, our country—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:37.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei(Overlap),0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This country produces \Nwine and dairy products,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:40.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei(Overlap),0000,0000,0000,,so you'll be seeing a lot \Nof nature and pastures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:45.40,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot about this country, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:50.02,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Mei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:53.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun, you're not saying much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:56.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:58.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this might happen, \Nso I brought some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:04.81,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:08.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Portable Frame, Type-L4,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Nendoro Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Please call me Ruri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:13.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:16.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:21.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, what's on your head, Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,That's my bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:28.68,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.45,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Really big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.22,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:30.84,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Super big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:32.08,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Totally big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.96,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,So big.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.68,big_14:33,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Big
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.68,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Big...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:46.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the car, again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:05.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:09.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Given that you're on this train,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:12.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you're somehow \Nrelated to the royal family, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:12.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:16.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,I would guess that he is a classmate \Nof the 13th crown princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Maid,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Nanami, \Ncurrently studying abroad in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:22.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a haniwa, \Na Japanese funeral doll, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What? A haniwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:29.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a ninja, then, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:34.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I have a friend named Ninjabayashi, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:40.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:46.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:50.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the 14th crown princess of \Nthe Principality of Bladefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:55.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Hakua Berserker Bladefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:00.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hakua...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my name is Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:07.54,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much like a haniwa, pretty much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Only the "ha" is the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:13.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lot of fun, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think you're
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,far more interesting than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:23.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please tell me \Nabout Japan, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,So in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:31.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,men and women go to the same school, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:33.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this country is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:36.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been, so I don't know, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Then why were you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:41.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I've been learning at a girls-only
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:43.31,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,nunnery since I was small, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:46.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you've been really sheltered, \Ncompared to Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:51.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, just like Nanami, \Nyou have a Japanese-ish name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my mother's Japanese, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:59.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,13th crown princess's mother is, as well, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:01.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So does that mean that you and \NNanami have different mothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.10,0:17:05.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have just asked \Nthat out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not normal to be siblings,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:09.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,but be born to different mothers, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess polygamy is normal for royalty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So, how old are you, Hakua?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:20.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be 16 this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the same age as Nanami and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:26.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you asked how old I was because Japan \Nbases their social structure off of age,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:29.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,and you wanted to see if \NI was inferior to you, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:29.69,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:37.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nanami! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this might happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:43.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,so I put a transmitter in your body. Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:49.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't come back, so I came \Nto see what was going on, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.81,0:17:54.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to extend my greetings \Nto you, 13th crown princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I extend my apologies for my companion's intrusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:57.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,14th crown princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:18:00.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure formal to each other for sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:04.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I've actually only met her a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:08.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Also, unlike me, the 14th crown \Nprincess is the youngest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,She was completely spoiled by His Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:15.01,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,His Majesty? Her father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:19.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking being so friendly \Nwith the 14th crown princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Akane and the others were
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,MaidD,0000,0000,0000,,You are in the presence of the princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:23.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}worried sick that you hadn't returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:23.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,MaidD,0000,0000,0000,,Please return—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:28.17,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate Princess Nanami and Princess Hakua.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.17,0:18:28.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,MaidH,0000,0000,0000,,An attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,MaidA,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, please run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:31.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:40.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I will complete my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:50.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hakua!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:58.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,MaidH,0000,0000,0000,,Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:00.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:17.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,My main body is undergoing maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:20.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably a mass-produced \Nunit that was exported to Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:24.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I believe she's been customized \Nto be an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:29.44,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,She may be a mass-produced unit, \Nbut she is my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:30.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I will take responsibility \Nas her older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:36.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I figured this'd happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:46.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:50.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last car, Souta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.94,0:19:51.94,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.15,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the same as...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:52.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You run to the end of the train,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:57.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,break the coupling, and activate the breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:20:59.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a typical running away flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:03.07,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You knew this was going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:05.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've \Nused it this way, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:08.58,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do something to a specific person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:12.22,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It's a stronger power than \NI've been using so far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:13.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:18.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,So she was an assassin, she was!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:22.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you plan on doing, Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:27.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:13.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:14.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Hakua, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.34,0:23:17.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought I'd \Nbe running away with princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.36,0:23:20.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't forget there was \Nanother princess here, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.93,0:23:24.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,When there are two princesses like \Nthis, one of them's usually a fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.52,0:23:25.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm real!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.46,0:23:27.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe the older sister \Nprotects the younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,and then gets captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:30.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're just messing with me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:31.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
